      • askForSelection

        @Nullable
private <T> T askForSelection​(java.lang.String questionText,
                              java.util.Collection<T> optionCollection,
                              boolean skippable)
        Method used for interacting with the user. It asks a question and wait for a valid user selection between the available options
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of the options
        Parameters:
        questionText - the text of the question
        optionCollection - the available options to choose from
        skippable - indicates whether or not the answer can be none of the available options
        Returns:
        the selected option or null if the user decided to skip
